data.description: Discover a spacious home that combines modern comfort with classic charm. A first-floor master bedroom and bathroom make daily living easy. Enjoy low-maintenance laminate flooring throughout. The large living room with vaulted ceiling allows plenty of natural light and warmth into the heart of the home, making it perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The generous yard is ideal for outdoor gatherings and fun. Upstairs, an ample bathroom with a washer and dryer adds convenience. A new metal roof and gutters provide both style and protection, ensuring peace of mind for years to come!
